description: This is an entry point JavaScript file for a React application. It sets up the root DOM node, renders the main App component within React StrictMode, and imports essential dependencies including React, ReactDOM, a CSS file, and the main App component.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React DOM node for rendering the React application.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the root DOM node.
